General.Name: Keyarch Acquisition Corporation Unit
General.Description: Keyarch Acquisition Corporation does not have significant operations. It focuses on effecting a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. The company intends to focus on disruptive technology and innovative services companies worldwide. Keyarch Acquisition Corporation was incorporated in 2021 and is based in New York, New York.
